entries.title_d: Destroy the next Prison Break Shuttle that is attempting to leave the Dathomir system. The prison break was a coordinated effort. Multiple ships are leaving the surface at the same time. Another one is trying to make a break for it. Catch and destroy it before it can leave the system.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Prison Break Shuttle. Part II
entries.split_quest_alert: Alert! Enemy engaged by TIE 701st wing. Enemy strength under estimated and the wing is in trouble. Request immediate assistance.
entries.quest_target_d: Intercept and destroy the prison break vessel before it can leave the system.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dathomir system and intercept the Prison Break Shuttle.
entries.quest_escort_d: Any ships with this vessel are enemies of the Empire. Destroy them.
entries.failed_escape: You have failed your Emperor. Report this failure to your superior and hope he has mercy to spare.
entries.destroy_escort: There are still some of the escorts that flew with the escaping vessel remaining. Destroy them. Destroy them all.
entries.assassinate_success: Excellent, pilot. You have done well. Those who try to violate the will of the Emperor have met their just fate.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Ship has reached orbit. This vessel and all traveling with her must also be destroyed.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Ship launch detected on planet surface. Stand by for interception coordinates.
